      <title>安大略省教师退休基金会首席执行官看好收购廉价欧洲资产的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ontario-teachers-ceo-sees-chance-to-snap-up-cheap-european-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安大略省教师退休金计划首席执行官表示，由于其他投资者仍关注美国，该计划正将更多注意力转向欧洲市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ontario-teachers-ceo-sees-chance-to-snap-up-cheap-european-assets</guid>
